# Event and community seed content (displayed from DB)
msgid "Trip to Galway with a Castle Visit"
msgstr "Trip to Galway with a Castle Visit"

msgid "Join us for an amazing day trip to Galway! We will visit the historic Dunguaire Castle, explore the colorful streets of Galway city, and enjoy traditional Irish music in a local pub."
msgstr "Join us for an amazing day trip to Galway! We will visit the historic Dunguaire Castle, explore the colorful streets of Galway city, and enjoy traditional Irish music in a local pub."

msgid "Wicklow Mountains Hiking Trip"
msgstr "Wicklow Mountains Hiking Trip"

msgid "Experience the breathtaking beauty of the Wicklow Mountains. This moderate-level hike takes us through Glendalough valley with stunning views of the upper and lower lakes."
msgstr "Experience the breathtaking beauty of the Wicklow Mountains. This moderate-level hike takes us through Glendalough valley with stunning views of the upper and lower lakes."

msgid "Wednesday Filming Locations Tour in Wicklow"
msgstr "Wednesday Filming Locations Tour in Wicklow"

msgid "Explore the magical filming locations of the Wednesday series in County Wicklow. Visit the stunning landscapes that served as the backdrop for Nevermore Academy."
msgstr "Explore the magical filming locations of the Wednesday series in County Wicklow. Visit the stunning landscapes that served as the backdrop for Nevermore Academy."

msgid "International Meetup in Dublin"
msgstr "International Meetup in Dublin"

msgid "Meet people from all over the world living in Dublin! This casual meetup is perfect for newcomers and anyone looking to expand their social circle in the city."
msgstr "Meet people from all over the world living in Dublin! This casual meetup is perfect for newcomers and anyone looking to expand their social circle in the city."

msgid "Language Exchange Night"
msgstr "Language Exchange Night"

msgid "Practice languages while making new friends! Bring your enthusiasm for learning and share your native language. All levels welcome."
msgstr "Practice languages while making new friends! Bring your enthusiasm for learning and share your native language. All levels welcome."

msgid "Photography Walk"
msgstr "Photography Walk"

msgid "Join fellow photography enthusiasts for a guided walk through Dublin's most photogenic spots. Bring any camera — phone cameras are welcome too!"
msgstr "Join fellow photography enthusiasts for a guided walk through Dublin's most photogenic spots. Bring any camera — phone cameras are welcome too!"

msgid "Coffee Meetup for Newcomers in Ireland"
msgstr "Coffee Meetup for Newcomers in Ireland"

msgid "New to Ireland? Come for a relaxed coffee meetup and meet other newcomers. Share tips, stories, and make lasting connections over great coffee."
msgstr "New to Ireland? Come for a relaxed coffee meetup and meet other newcomers. Share tips, stories, and make lasting connections over great coffee."

msgid "Pub Social Night"
msgstr "Pub Social Night"

msgid "Experience the famous Irish pub culture! Join us for a fun night of live music, great craic, and the best Guinness in town."
msgstr "Experience the famous Irish pub culture! Join us for a fun night of live music, great craic, and the best Guinness in town."

msgid "Art and Creativity Workshop"
msgstr "Art and Creativity Workshop"

msgid "Unleash your creative side in this hands-on art workshop. No experience needed — just bring your curiosity and willingness to try something new!"
msgstr "Unleash your creative side in this hands-on art workshop. No experience needed — just bring your curiosity and willingness to try something new!"

msgid "Language Exchange Community"
msgstr "Language Exchange Community"

msgid "Connect with language learners and native speakers. Practice your target language in a friendly, supportive environment through regular meetups and events."
msgstr "Connect with language learners and native speakers. Practice your target language in a friendly, supportive environment through regular meetups and events."

msgid "Hiking Ireland"
msgstr "Hiking Ireland"

msgid "Explore Ireland's stunning trails and mountains together. From gentle coastal walks to challenging mountain hikes, there's something for everyone."
msgstr "Explore Ireland's stunning trails and mountains together. From gentle coastal walks to challenging mountain hikes, there's something for everyone."

msgid "International Friends in Dublin"
msgstr "International Friends in Dublin"

msgid "A welcoming community for internationals living in Dublin. Meet people from around the world, share experiences, and build lasting friendships."
msgstr "A welcoming community for internationals living in Dublin. Meet people from around the world, share experiences, and build lasting friendships."

msgid "Photography Club"
msgstr "Photography Club"

msgid "For photographers of all levels! Share your work, learn new techniques, and join photo walks around Ireland's most beautiful locations."
msgstr "For photographers of all levels! Share your work, learn new techniques, and join photo walks around Ireland's most beautiful locations."

msgid "Tech and Startups Ireland"
msgstr "Tech and Startups Ireland"

msgid "Connect with tech professionals, startup founders, and anyone interested in the Irish tech scene. Networking events, talks, and hackathons."
msgstr "Connect with tech professionals, startup founders, and anyone interested in the Irish tech scene. Networking events, talks, and hackathons."

msgid "Art and Creativity"
msgstr "Art and Creativity"

msgid "A space for artists, creatives, and art enthusiasts. From painting workshops to gallery visits, let creativity bring us together."
msgstr "A space for artists, creatives, and art enthusiasts. From painting workshops to gallery visits, let creativity bring us together."

msgid "Travel Buddies"
msgstr "Travel Buddies"

msgid "Find travel companions for adventures around Ireland and beyond. Share travel tips, plan group trips, and explore new destinations together."
msgstr "Find travel companions for adventures around Ireland and beyond. Share travel tips, plan group trips, and explore new destinations together."
